CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,FFailure at Stormont to agree a multi-
OL,8,Fyear budget will make a major
OL,9,Ftransformation of the health service
OL,10,Fharder to deliver, a senior official
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FThe Stormont Executive has yet to
OL,14,Fagree its first multi-year budget in
OL,15,Fmore than a decade despite Finance
OL,16,FMinister John O'Dowd publishing draft
OL,17,Fproposals in January.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,FMike Farrar, permanent secretary at
OL,8,Fthe Department of Health, said while
OL,9,Fthe health reset plan can be delivered
OL,10,Fin single-year budgets, it will be
OL,11,Fmore difficult than with a three-year
OL,12,Fbudget which allows for more long-term
OL,13,Fplans.
OL,15,FHealth currently consumes more than
OL,16,F50% of Northern Ireland's annual
OL,17,Fbudget.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,FMr Farrar has warned this is set to
OL,8,Fincrease to 75% by 2025 unless the
OL,9,Fservice is transformed, adding he does
OL,10,Fnot believe it is feasible to keep
OL,11,Fgoing to the Executive asking for more
OL,12,Fmoney at the expense of other
OL,13,Fdepartments.
OL,15,FThe health budget started the last
OL,16,Ffinancial year with a #600 million
OL,17,Fshortfall, which was resolved with the
OL,18,Ffinding of almost #300 million in
OL,19,Fsavings, as well as help from the
OL,20,FExecutive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,FIt is set to start the next financial
OL,8,Fyear with an #800 million projected
OL,9,Fshortfall.
OL,11,FThis includes additional demand, staff
OL,12,Fcosts, tariffs on drugs and inflation.
OL,14,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt published
OL,15,Fhis reset plan last July.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,FAs part of this, there will be a focus
OL,8,Fon spending more money on
OL,9,Fneighbourhood care, with the aim of
OL,10,Fkeeping people out of hospitals, as
OL,11,Fwell as a new public health message
OL,12,Finitiative aimed at stopping people
OL,13,Fbecoming sick.
OL,15,FMike Farrar told UTV that without a
OL,16,Fthree-year funding plan, it's going to
OL,17,Fbe harder to deliver the much-needed
OL,18,Ftransformation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,FMany of the things that people across
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland are currently
OL,9,Fexperiencing, such as difficulties
OL,10,Faccessing GP appointments, overcrowded
OL,11,Femergency departments, and long waits
OL,12,Ffor treatment, could continue for much
OL,13,Flonger.
OL,15,FMike Farrar said: "It will delay our
OL,16,Fability to change the way we provide
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774954972
OL,3,CMajor health service reset 'will be
OL,4,Cmore difficult without multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget'
OL,7,F"So we will continue some of the
OL,8,Fproblems we have now where too many
OL,9,Fpeople end up in hospital, where they
OL,10,Fcan't get GP access, where all those
OL,11,Fthings that are causing difficulty now.
OL,13,F"We won't be able to change and
OL,14,Fimprove that because that little bit
OL,15,Fof money and certainty over a three-
OL,16,Fyear period allows us to profile our
OL,17,Fspending and deliver those changes."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
